00:06:08.320 --> 00:06:09.720
was cast out

00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:13.040
after He Jiu's downfall.

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:15.400
As for Pei Xun,

00:06:15.880 --> 00:06:17.560
after learning his true identity,

00:06:18.200 --> 00:06:20.280
he took Pei Qishan down with him.

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:26.640
Time flies so fast.

00:06:27.280 --> 00:06:28.760
A decade in the blink of an eye.

00:06:34.160 --> 00:06:35.400
Look at this leg of mine.

00:06:38.880 --> 00:06:40.920
If I keep clinging to the police force,

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:43.360
