00:06:45.160 --> 00:06:47.800
"You're a cop,
yet you can't even catch a thief!"

00:06:49.480 --> 00:06:50.720
Therefore,

00:06:51.920 --> 00:06:53.160
from now on,

00:06:54.080 --> 00:06:55.640
I decided to stay right here with you.

